{"tid":1013914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【快簽禁令？】傳特朗普趕絕中國電訊設備","createTime":"2019-02-08T17:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T03:35:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ae691512129bc96b503fcb7f21024b73a6bb7e10","tid":1013914,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】據外國媒體報道，美國總統特朗普將會簽署針對中國電訊設備商的行政禁令。<br />\n<br />\n美國政治新聞網站Politico引述多個消息指，特朗普計劃於2月25日至27日，世界互聯網大會前發布一項行政命令，禁止美國網絡採用中國電訊設備。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，美國希望透過這個全球最大型的互聯網行業會議，傳遞未來的尖端科技發展，必需首要考慮網絡安全訊息，不過，這舉動或影響到中美關係，白宮拒絕回應有關傳聞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=336910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336910&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1GHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=46752fa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336910&h=35bb587a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=336910</a>"},{"pid":"483a2cebbe21f24f8c80f62bdd0e56b7feacecfe","tid":1013914,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891c48f0f3bbca0003aadea8d19529861388ae9a","tid":1013914,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T17:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b296657f79f6668631c0cfca8f5b1b8e44c02f","tid":1013914,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgm